{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775898811302,"sessionID":"ses_2842ef4e0ffeoBcV4suEXEi79D","part":{"id":"prt_d7bd1536c0019mgyJdMoumDjy5","messageID":"msg_d7bd13047001X9WvCu28WyfMqs","sessionID":"ses_2842ef4e0ffeoBcV4suEXEi79D","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_functions.read:5","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-025/delta-spec.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-025/delta-spec.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-025: MetadataService 与数据模型 — Delta Spec\n2: \n3: ## Overview\n4: This document describes the delta specification for implementing the MetadataService\n5: and data models in the cmd/cli module.\n6: \n7: ## Current State\n8: - No centralized metadata management service\n9: - Metadata scattered in various configuration files\n10: - No schema validation for agent metadata\n11: - Limited search/query capabilities\n12: - No versioning for metadata changes\n13: \n14: ## Target State\n15: A unified MetadataService that:\n16: - Provides centralized metadata management\n17: - Enforces schema validation via Pydantic models\n18: - Supports versioning for audit and rollback\n19: - Enables search and filtering capabilities\n20: - Provides import/export functionality\n21: \n22: ## Delta Analysis\n23: \n24: ### New Components\n25: 1. **MetadataService** (`cmd/cli/internal/metadata_service.py`)\n26:    - Main service class for metadata operations\n27:    - CRUD operations with validation\n28:    - Search and query methods\n29: \n30: 2. **Data Models** (`cmd/cli/models/metadata.py`)\n31:    - Pydantic-based schema definitions\n32:    - AgentMetadata model\n33:    - MetadataVersion model\n34: \n35: 3. **Storage Interface** (`cmd/cli/internal/storage_interface.py`)\n36:    - Abstract storage interface\n37:    - Pluggable backend support\n38: \n39: 4. **Exceptions** (`cmd/cli/exceptions/metadata.py`)\n40:    - MetadataError base class\n41:    - ValidationError, NotFoundError, etc.\n42: \n43: ### Modified Components\n44: - None (this is a new service layer)\n45: \n46: ### Dependencies\n47: - pydantic library for data validation\n48: - Existing storage backends (file, database)\n49: \n50: ## Interface Specification\n51: \n52: ### MetadataService Class\n53: ```python\n54: class MetadataService:\n55:     def __init__(self, storage: MetadataStorage = None)\n56:     def create_metadata(self, data: dict) -> AgentMetadata\n57:     def get_metadata(self, metadata_id: str) -> AgentMetadata\n58:     def update_metadata(self, metadata_id: str, data: dict) -> AgentMetadata\n59:     def delete_metadata(self, metadata_id: str) -> None\n60:     def list_metadata(self, page: int = 1, page_size: int = 50) -> List[AgentMetadata]\n61:     def search_metadata(self, query: str, filters: dict = None) -> List[AgentMetadata]\n62:     def export_metadata(self, metadata_ids: List[str], filepath: str) -> None\n63:     def import_metadata(self, filepath: str) -> List[AgentMetadata]\n64: ```\n65: \n66: ## Implementation Notes\n67: - Use Pydantic v2 for validation\n68: - Support async operations where beneficial\n69: - Soft delete for data recovery\n70: - JSON format for import/export compatibility\n\n(End of file - total 70 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-025: MetadataService 与数据模型 — Delta Spec\n\n## Overview\nThis document describes the delta specification for implementing the MetadataService\nand data models in the cmd/cli module.\n\n## Current State\n- No centralized metadata management service\n- Metadata scattered in various configuration files\n- No schema validation for agent metadata\n- Limited search/query capabilities\n- No versioning for metadata changes\n\n## Target State\nA unified MetadataService that:\n- Provides centralized metadata management\n- Enforces schema validation via Pydantic models\n- Supports versioning for audit and rollback\n- Enables search and filtering capabilities\n- Provides import/export functionality","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-025/delta-spec.md","time":{"start":1775898811272,"end":1775898811300}}}}
