{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775898828803,"sessionID":"ses_2842ef4e0ffeoBcV4suEXEi79D","part":{"id":"prt_d7bd18056001khCawDB0QlRVCm","messageID":"msg_d7bd15bee001vM0tYU6lq3zceH","sessionID":"ses_2842ef4e0ffeoBcV4suEXEi79D","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_functions.read:6","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-025/design.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-025/design.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-025: MetadataService 与数据模型 — Design Document\n2: \n3: ## Architecture\n4: \n5: ### Component Diagram\n6: ```\n7: ┌─────────────────┐\n8: │   CLI Commands  │\n9: │ (agent, config) │\n10: └────────┬────────┘\n11:          │\n12: ┌────────▼────────┐\n13: │ MetadataService │\n14: │(metadata_service│\n15: └────────┬────────┘\n16:          │\n17:     ┌────┴────┐\n18:     ▼         ▼\n19: ┌───────┐ ┌───────┐\n20: │Schema │ │Storage│\n21: │Validator│ │Interface\n22: └───┬───┘ └────┬──┘\n23:     │          │\n24:     ▼          ▼\n25: ┌─────────┐ ┌─────────┐\n26: │Pydantic │ │ Storage │\n27: │Models   │ │ Backend │\n28: └─────────┘ └─────────┘\n29: ```\n30: \n31: ## Key Design Decisions\n32: \n33: ### Data Model Design\n34: - Use Pydantic models for schema definition and validation\n35: - Base metadata model with extensible fields\n36: - Version tracking with timestamps\n37: - Soft delete support for data recovery\n38: \n39: ### Storage Abstraction\n40: - Interface-based storage layer\n41: - Support for multiple backends (file, database)\n42: - Async operations for I/O bound tasks\n43: - Connection pooling where applicable\n44: \n45: ### Schema Validation\n46: - JSON Schema compatible validation\n47: - Custom business rule validators\n48: - Detailed error messages with field paths\n49: - Pre-save validation hooks\n50: \n51: ### Versioning Strategy\n52: - Incremental version numbers\n53: - Timestamp tracking for audit\n54: - Change history preservation\n55: - Rollback capability\n56: \n57: ## Data Flow\n58: 1. CLI command calls MetadataService method\n59: 2. Service validates input parameters\n60: 3. Schema validation against Pydantic models\n61: 4. Execute storage operation via interface\n62: 5. Return structured result or raise exception\n\n(End of file - total 62 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-025: MetadataService 与数据模型 — Design Document\n\n## Architecture\n\n### Component Diagram\n```\n┌─────────────────┐\n│   CLI Commands  │\n│ (agent, config) │\n└────────┬────────┘\n         │\n┌────────▼────────┐\n│ MetadataService │\n│(metadata_service│\n└────────┬────────┘\n         │\n    ┌────┴────┐\n    ▼         ▼\n┌───────┐ ┌───────┐\n│Schema │ │Storage│","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-025/design.md","time":{"start":1775898828777,"end":1775898828801}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775898828804,"sessionID":"ses_2842ef4e0ffeoBcV4suEXEi79D","part":{"id":"prt_d7bd1887f001Ijsns11F29ho1c","messageID":"msg_d7bd15bee001vM0tYU6lq3zceH","sessionID":"ses_2842ef4e0ffeoBcV4suEXEi79D","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_functions.read:7","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-025/plan.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-025/plan.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-025: MetadataService 与数据模型 — Implementation Plan\n2: \n3: ## Phase 1: Foundation\n4: - [ ] Create MetadataService class structure\n5: - [ ] Define data model schemas using Pydantic\n6: - [ ] Implement storage interface abstraction\n7: - [ ] Set up configuration management\n8: \n9: ## Phase 2: Core CRUD Operations\n10: - [ ] Implement metadata creation with validation\n11: - [ ] Implement metadata retrieval by ID\n12: - [ ] Implement metadata update with versioning\n13: - [ ] Implement metadata deletion (soft delete)\n14: - [ ] Implement metadata listing with pagination\n15: \n16: ## Phase 3: Schema & Validation\n17: - [ ] Define agent metadata schema\n18: - [ ] Implement schema validation logic\n19: - [ ] Add custom validators for business rules\n20: - [ ] Handle validation error messages\n21: \n22: ## Phase 4: Search & Query\n23: - [ ] Implement basic search by keyword\n24: - [ ] Add filter support (by type, status, tags)\n25: - [ ] Implement sorting options\n26: - [ ] Add pagination for search results\n27: \n28: ## Phase 5: Import/Export\n29: - [ ] Implement metadata export to JSON\n30: - [ ] Implement metadata import from JSON\n31: - [ ] Add validation during import\n32: - [ ] Handle import error recovery\n33: \n34: ## Phase 6: Error Handling & Testing\n35: - [ ] Define custom exception hierarchy\n36: - [ ] Implement comprehensive error handling\n37: - [ ] Write unit tests with mocks\n38: - [ ] Write integration tests\n\n(End of file - total 38 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-025: MetadataService 与数据模型 — Implementation Plan\n\n## Phase 1: Foundation\n- [ ] Create MetadataService class structure\n- [ ] Define data model schemas using Pydantic\n- [ ] Implement storage interface abstraction\n- [ ] Set up configuration management\n\n## Phase 2: Core CRUD Operations\n- [ ] Implement metadata creation with validation\n- [ ] Implement metadata retrieval by ID\n- [ ] Implement metadata update with versioning\n- [ ] Implement metadata deletion (soft delete)\n- [ ] Implement metadata listing with pagination\n\n## Phase 3: Schema & Validation\n- [ ] Define agent metadata schema\n- [ ] Implement schema validation logic\n- [ ] Add custom validators for business rules\n- [ ] Handle validation error messages","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-025/plan.md","time":{"start":1775898828781,"end":1775898828803}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775898828806,"sessionID":"ses_2842ef4e0ffeoBcV4suEXEi79D","part":{"id":"prt_d7bd18fb8001pSYYUxuxQDV2cK","messageID":"msg_d7bd15bee001vM0tYU6lq3zceH","sessionID":"ses_2842ef4e0ffeoBcV4suEXEi79D","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_functions.read:8","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-025/tests.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-025/tests.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-025: MetadataService 与数据模型 — Test Specification\n2: \n3: ## Unit Tests\n4: \n5: ### Service Initialization Tests\n6: - `test_initializes_with_storage`: Storage interface injected correctly\n7: - `test_initializes_with_default_storage`: Default storage created when none provided\n8: - `test_logger_configuration`: Logger set based on verbose flag\n9: - `test_raises_on_invalid_storage`: Error when storage doesn't implement interface\n10: \n11: ### Data Model Tests\n12: - `test_agent_metadata_valid`: Valid metadata passes validation\n13: - `test_agent_metadata_invalid_name`: Invalid name raises ValidationError\n14: - `test_agent_metadata_missing_required`: Missing required fields raises error\n15: - `test_version_increment`: Version increases on update\n16: - `test_timestamps_auto_set`: Created/updated timestamps populated\n17: \n18: ### CRUD Operation Tests\n19: - `test_create_metadata_returns_with_id`: Created metadata has ID assigned\n20: - `test_create_metadata_validates_input`: Invalid input raises ValidationError\n21: - `test_get_metadata_by_id`: Retrieval by ID returns correct metadata\n22: - `test_get_metadata_not_found_raises`: Missing ID raises NotFoundError\n23: - `test_update_metadata_increments_version`: Version incremented on update\n24: - `test_update_metadata_updates_timestamp`: Updated timestamp refreshed\n25: - `test_delete_metadata_soft_delete`: Marked deleted, not removed\n26: - `test_delete_metadata_not_found_raises`: Missing ID raises NotFoundError\n27: - `test_list_metadata_returns_paginated`: Paginated results returned\n28: - `test_list_metadata_respects_page_size`: Page size honored\n29: \n30: ### Search & Filter Tests\n31: - `test_search_by_keyword_returns_matches`: Keyword search finds matches\n32: - `test_search_by_keyword_no_matches`: Empty results when no matches\n33: - `test_filter_by_type`: Type filter returns correct subset\n34: - `test_filter_by_status`: Status filter working\n35: - `test_filter_by_tags`: Tag filtering returns matching metadata\n36: - `test_filter_combination`: Multiple filters combined with AND\n37: - `test_sort_by_created_asc`: Sort by created ascending\n38: - `test_sort_by_name_desc`: Sort by name descending\n39: \n40: ### Import/Export Tests\n41: - `test_export_metadata_to_json`: JSON file created with correct content\n42: - `test_export_multiple_metadata`: Batch export working\n43: - `test_import_metadata_from_json`: Metadata created from JSON\n44: - `test_import_validates_data`: Invalid JSON raises ValidationError\n45: - `test_import_preserves_id`: ID preserved when specified\n46: - `test_import_generates_id_when_missing`: New ID assigned when not specified\n47: \n48: ### Error Handling Tests\n49: - `test_validation_error_includes_field_path`: Error message has field path\n50: - `test_storage_error_wrapped`: Storage errors wrapped in MetadataError\n51: - `test_concurrent_update_handled`: Concurrent modification handled gracefully\n52: \n53: ## Integration Tests\n54: \n55: ### Happy Path\n56: - `test_full_metadata_lifecycle`: Create → Read → Update → Delete\n57: - `test_search_and_filter_workflow`: Create multiple, search, filter\n58: - `test_import_export_roundtrip`: Export then import preserves data\n59: \n60: ### Error Scenarios\n61: - `test_duplicate_id_handling`: Duplicate ID handled appropriately\n62: - `test_corrupted_storage_recovery`: Graceful handling of storage errors\n63: - `test_concurrent_modification`: Last-write-wins or conflict detection\n64: \n65: ## Test Data\n66: - Sample agent metadata fixtures\n67: - Invalid metadata for validation testing\n68: - Mock storage implementation\n69: - Test JSON files for import/export\n\n(End of file - total 69 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-025: MetadataService 与数据模型 — Test Specification\n\n## Unit Tests\n\n### Service Initialization Tests\n- `test_initializes_with_storage`: Storage interface injected correctly\n- `test_initializes_with_default_storage`: Default storage created when none provided\n- `test_logger_configuration`: Logger set based on verbose flag\n- `test_raises_on_invalid_storage`: Error when storage doesn't implement interface\n\n### Data Model Tests\n- `test_agent_metadata_valid`: Valid metadata passes validation\n- `test_agent_metadata_invalid_name`: Invalid name raises ValidationError\n- `test_agent_metadata_missing_required`: Missing required fields raises error\n- `test_version_increment`: Version increases on update\n- `test_timestamps_auto_set`: Created/updated timestamps populated\n\n### CRUD Operation Tests\n- `test_create_metadata_returns_with_id`: Created metadata has ID assigned\n- `test_create_metadata_validates_input`: Invalid input raises ValidationError","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-025/tests.md","time":{"start":1775898828784,"end":1775898828805}}}}
