n| **Pagination** | Not implemented — no page/page_size support | `metadata_service.py` |\n| **Import/Export (JSON)** | Not implemented — no `import_metadata()`, `export_metadata()` methods | `metadata_service.py` |\n| **Storage Interface Abstraction** | Not implemented — no `MetadataStorage` ABC for pluggable backends | `storage_interface.py` |\n| **Custom Exception Hierarchy** | Not implemented — only using built-in exceptions and Pydantic errors | `exceptions/metadata.py` |\n| **Integration Tests** | Not implemented — only unit tests exist | `tests/integration/` |\n| **Filter by type/status/tags** | Not implemented | `metadata_service.py` |\n| **Sorting options** | Not implemented — no sort_by parameter | `metadata_service.py` |\n\n---\n\n### Summary\n\nThe **core data model and basic CRUD operations** are fully implemented and tested. The service provides a solid foundation for agent metadata management with proper validation and file I/O.\n\nThe **advanced features** (versioning, search/query, import/export, storage abstraction) were scoped but not implemented in this archive.","time":{"start":1775898873246,"end":1775898873246}}}
